<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>The Debugger's Digest</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial;
            margin: 0;
            background: #f4f7fb;
        }

        header {
            background: #2c3e50;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px;
        }

        header h1 {
            margin: 0;
        }

        nav ul {
            list-style: none;
            display: flex;
            gap: 15px;
            padding: 0;
        }

        nav a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .container {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 3fr 1fr;
            gap: 20px;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        article {
            background: white;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        article:hover {
            transform: scale(1.02);
        }

        a {
            color: #2980b9;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        button {
            background: #2980b9;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 6px 10px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        aside {
            background: white;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px;
            background: #2c3e50;
            color: white;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <header>
        <h1>The Debugger's Digest</h1>
        <nav>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="#">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">Latest Articles</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">Contact</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </header>
    <main class="container">
        <section>
            <h2>Featured Posts</h2>
            <article>
                <h3>The Rise of Semantic HTML</h3>
                <p><small>Published on October 24, 2023</small></p>

                <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/600x250" alt="Example of semantic HTML structure">

                <p>Semantic HTML improves accessibility and structure of webpages...</p>

                <a href="#">Read full article →</a>
            </article>
            <article>
                <h3>Accessibility: More Than Just Alt Text</h3>
                <p><small>Published on October 22, 2023</small></p>

                <p>Accessibility includes color contrast, navigation and structure...</p>

                <a href="#">Read full article →</a>
            </article>
        </section>
        <aside>
            <h3>Related Links</h3>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="https://w3.org/WAI/">W3C Accessibility</a></li>
                <li><a href="https://developer.mozilla.org/">MDN Docs</a></li>
            </ul>
            <hr>
            <h3>Newsletter</h3>
            <form>
                <label for="email">Email:</label><br>
                <input type="email" id="email" required><br><br>
                <button>Subscribe</button>
            </form>
        </aside>
    </main>
    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2023 The Debugger's Digest</p>
    </footer>
</body>

</html>
